oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wiliam Sullivan, of Hixon, Tenn., with 28 lb. drum caught at Watts Bar Dam
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of William Sullivan of Route 1, Hixon, Tenn., with a 28 lb. drum caught at the "glory hole" at Watts Bar Dam. The fish measured thirty-eight inches long with a girth of 25� Sullivan is wearing a hat, eyeglasses, coat and pants.
